{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/story.png?t=1737278919\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a quest to find the parts of your crashed ship as you battle ruthless enemies and uncover the secrets of your true identity. Explore a variety of biomes, each teeming with fearsome creatures. Unlock unique abilities to refine your combat strategy and take on epic bosses with demanding mechanics that invite you to adapt your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/explore_and_sicover.png?t=1737278919\" />     <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/steam_gif_explore.gif?t=1737278919\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cell-Shaded Cutscenes:</strong> Immerse yourself in a captivating story that reveals Atrion's identity and role in this chaotic universe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Varied Levels:</strong> Enjoy distinct environments and unique enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/electronic_synth.png?t=1737278919\" />     <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/fight_gif.gif?t=1737278919\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fast-Paced, Intense Combat:</strong> Execute fluid combos in dynamic confrontations, accompanied by the rhythm of electro/synthwave music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451700/extras/kill_die.png?t=17372